UID: ZEP-SRS-1-13
STATUS: Draft
TYPE: Functional
COMPONENT: Threads
TITLE: Defining a thread at compile time
STATEMENT: >>>
The Zephyr RTOS shall provide an interface to define a thread at compile time.
<<<
RELATIONS:
