UID: ZEP-SRS-1-14
STATUS: Draft
TYPE: Functional
COMPONENT: Threads
TITLE: Starting an inactive thread
STATEMENT: >>>
The Zephyr RTOS shall provide an interface to start a thread that was created without being scheduled to start.
<<<
